title: Roy Lichtenstein Boxed Note Cards
description:
Send your best wishes with the beautifully reproduced artwork on these full-color full-size Notecard Boxes, packaged in a large format 2 piece glossy reusable box.

This Roy Lichtenstein Notecard Box highlights the best of this pop artist's career. Ideal for fans of comics and the 60s, these beautiful notecards feature bright colors and bold lines.

  • Dimensions: 7.5 x 5.5 x 1.5 in.
  • Materials: 20 envelopes & 20 notecards, 5 each of 4 images
